          <span class="arrow">&gt;</span>
          [HXTCH]
        </div>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
          an electronic music festival outfit based in Cox's Bazar, Bangladesh co-founded in 2021 by Ishaq Sikder, Mridul Moinak and Rashad Wajahat, pushing the emergence of a nascent electronic music scene in Bangladesh by curating eccentric sounds for inclusive spaces where diverse communities come together to dance, absorb electronic music, explore individual self-expression, and discover collective liberation. Rashad leads the team on all things aesthetic, ranging from digital content to live visuals. follow their events on instagram
          <a href="https://instagram.com/hxtch.me" target="_blank" style="color:#fff; text-decoration:underline;">@hxtch.me</a>.
