            <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OezryXGBKWs?si=kHdQVcT5qjEf9ndY" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            <div class="yt-caption"><em>video edit by flimcadet</em></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="dropdown">
          <span class="arrow">&gt;</span>
          audiovisual performance // vj
        </div>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
          immersive audiovisual works combining sound, video, and realtime generative visuals for live performance.
          <div class="yt-stack">
            <div class="yt-embed">
              <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tj6TOI_a9zs?si=8NoyWwerfkOmKRoM" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="yt-embed">
              <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uad6dN-sisI?si=4p1y5IGquT6d6chx" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="yt-embed">
              <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SlWqGVxvEb4?si=Arpn_BsGUlR4JmF6" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="dropdown">
          <span class="arrow">&gt;</span>
          Moshari (2022)
        </div>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
          Rashad Wajahat served as executive producer on writer-director Nuhash Humayun's horror short film <strong>Moshari (2022)</strong>,
          <a href="https://variety.com/2022/film/global/jordan-peele-riz-ahmed-moshari-nuhash-humayuns-1235440579/" target="_blank" style="color:#fff; text-decoration:underline;">
            joined by executive producers Jordan Peele and Riz Ahmed</a>
          after an award-winning festival run.<br><br>
          <em>"Two sisters are forced inside a mosquito net (moshari) to survive â€” but can they survive each other?"</em>
          <div class="video-embed">
            <div style="padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;">
              <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/759653578?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; web-share" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;" title="MOSHARI"></iframe>
            </div>
            <script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <script>
    // Dropdown functionality
    document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown').forEach(function(drop) {
      drop.addEventListener('click', function() {
        var li = drop.parentElement;
        document.querySelectorAll('ul > li').forEach(function(otherLi) {
          if (otherLi !== li) otherLi.classList.remove('open');
        });
        li.classList.toggle('open');
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
